Subject: [PATCH 1/3] Optimize PDF generation with expanded 7-8 page
 comprehensive application documents

- Optimized font sizes and spacing for professional 7-8 page PDFs
- Expanded KYC/AML documentation with detailed requirements
- Added comprehensive SWIFT and cryptocurrency payment instructions with full bank details
- Enhanced Step 9 Review & Attestation with complete binding legal terms (A-J)
- Added application summary, document information, and processing notes sections
- Improved signature display and attestation container styling
- Updated header layout with application summary
- Optimized payment and third-party notice sections
- All content now includes full details for regulatory compliance and archival
- Generated PDFs now display professional 7-8 page documents with all content
